query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('cs')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('algorithm-analysis',
'algorithms',
'complexity-theory',
'formal-languages',
'graph-theory',
'graphs',
'optimization',
'time-complexity',
'turing-machines');
